<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Selamat Datang di Zyvent</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f7fa;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background: #7a7a73;
        color: white;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .brand {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-size: 15px;
        opacity: 0.9;
        font-weight: 300;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .welcome-text {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1f2937;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .description {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .user-info {
        background: #f9fafb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .info-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        padding-bottom: 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .info-row:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
        padding-bottom: 0;
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .info-label {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #374151;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .info-value {
        font-weight: 400;
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 14px;
        text-align: right;
      }

      .cta-section {
        background: #f3f4f6;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .cta-text {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #374151;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #7a7a73;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 32px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background: #57564f;
      }

      .notes {
        background: #eda35a;
        border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .notes-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #92400e;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .notes-list {
        color: #92400e;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .backup-link {
        background: #f3f4f6;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 12px;
        word-break: break-all;
        margin-top: 8px;
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .footer {
        background: #f9fafb;
        padding: 24px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .support-info {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .copyright {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #9ca3af;
        margin-top: 16px;
      }

      /* Mobile Responsiveness */
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        body {
          padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .container {
          margin: 0 10px;
          border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 32px 20px;
        }

        .brand {
          font-size: 22px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 32px 20px;
        }

        .welcome-text {
          font-size: 18px;
        }

        .description {
          font-size: 15px;
        }

        .user-info {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .info-row {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 4px;
        }

        .info-value {
          text-align: left;
          font-weight: 500;
        }

        .cta-section {
          padding: 24px 20px;
        }

        .btn {
          padding: 12px 24px;
          font-size: 15px;
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 280px;
        }

        .footer {
          padding: 20px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .container {
          margin: 0 5px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }

        .user-info {
          padding: 16px;
        }

        .cta-section {
          padding: 20px 16px;
        }

        .notes {
          padding: 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="brand">ZYVENT</div>
        <div class="tagline">Event Management Platform</div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="welcome-text">Halo <%= username %>!</h1>

        <p class="description">
          Terima kasih sudah mendaftar di Zyvent. Akun kamu sudah berhasil
          dibuat, tinggal satu langkah lagi untuk bisa mulai menggunakan semua
          fitur yang ada.
        </p>

        <div class="user-info">
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Nama: &emsp;</span>
            <span class="info-value"> <%= fullName %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Email: &emsp;</span>
            <span class="info-value"> <%= email %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Username: &emsp;</span>
            <span class="info-value">@<%= username %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Tanggal Daftar: &emsp;</span>
            <span class="info-value"><%= createdAt %></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-section">
          <p class="cta-text">Aktivasi akun untuk mulai menggunakan Zyvent</p>
          <a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="btn">Aktivasi Akun</a>
        </div>

        <div class="notes">
          <div class="notes-title">Penting untuk diperhatikan:</div>
          <div class="notes-list">
            • Link aktivasi berlaku selama 24 jam<br />
            • Kalau tombol tidak berfungsi, copy link di bawah ini:
            <div class="backup-link"><%= activationLink %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <div class="support-info">
          Ada pertanyaan? Hubungi kami di support@zyvent.com
        </div>
        <div class="copyright">
          © 2025 Zyvent. Email otomatis, mohon tidak dibalas.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
